CustomField.description: A Traverse Instruction contains key names to JSON paths. e.g. x$candidates[*].location.x. Multiple Instructions are separated using a semi-colon. Refer to the Wiki for details.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: A Traverse Instruction contains key names to JSONpaths. e.g. x,y$candidates[*].location["x","y"]. Multiple Instructions are separated using a ; symbol. Refer to the Wiki for details.
CustomField.label: Response Traverse Instructions
